  <brief_title>Adalimumab Intralesional in Intestinal Strictures of Crohn's Disease Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blinded, Placebo-controlled Study on the Effects of Adalimumab Intralesional Intestinal Strictures of Crohn's Disease Patients</official_title>
